name: Make Fishtail Braids
description:
Make Fishtail Braids is a fun-filled beauty hairstyle design game.
The fishtail braids have become a popular element this year,and now it seems that the hairstyles are classic and lovely.They became many girls's favorite style and also the one with higher head-turning.Let's know a fishtail braids through the game and learn the detailed steps that how to make it,get the way to this hairstyle in order to apply it in life.Have fun,enjoy your game

Game Features:
- You will find the way that how to get higher head-turing
- Learn the simple basic fishtail braids steps
- Well-designed game steps make you never want to stop
- Fluent and clearly frames,vivid and beautiful characters
- Comfortable color matching make you better enjoy this game
